With the primary match identified (Resolution 1656), I need to verify the new ward details.  I checked the "New wards" list for "Xã Hồng Vân" in "Thành phố Hà Nội" and found a perfect match:  `{"ward_code":"10210","ward_name":"Xã Hồng Vân","province_name":"Thành phố Hà Nội"}`.
